column5: Zone 16 pike and Walleye open 2nd sat in May which is the 8th correct?  Simcoe whitefish and lakers also open 2nd sat in May. Just want to make sure these species are open this Saturday.
Also saw this in exceptions:   Looks like you're good to go.
Yep, its go time on Simcoe this weekend. Need some company on Saturday?
not sure yet.  Thinking of going over to willow beach but weather is no cooperating.
Rain and high winds all day for tomorrow.  I think I will do some work around the house and wait for some better weather.
